Welcome to the ''TiddlyWiki Revision History'' plugin demo! 
This edition showcases the features of the plugin. 

Navigating to the [[Showcase]] tiddler will show you a tiddler with pre-populated history. Click the Revisions tab in the tiddler info panel to view it in action!
You can also try editing tiddlers or creating new ones, then returning to the Revisions tab to see the captured history and diffs.
